reference:
jsonObject- https://www.tutorialspoint.com/json/json_java_example.htm
jsonObject- https://www.baeldung.com/java-org-json
jackson-

Add dependency
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.json</groupId>
    <artifactId>json</artifactId>
    <version>20180130</version>
</dependency>

Jpa entities must be serializable at all time.
For serializing/deserializing objects we use jackson.
Public fields are serializable by default. In order to serialize/deserialize a private field it must have getter/setter.

